  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: var(--beeswax); line-height: 1.7;">If you want to know what a Byzantine Catholic is, the best answer is not on this page. It is in a church. Find a Byzantine Catholic parish near you. Attend a Sunday Divine Liturgy. You will understand more in one hour of worship than in any amount of reading. Come early. Stand if others stand. Follow the incense with your eyes. Let the chant wash over you. You will know.</p>
